org.svvrl.goal.core.comp.safra
Class SafraContainmentState

java.lang.Object
  org.svvrl.goal.core.comp.safra.SafraContainmentState

public class SafraContainmentState
extends java.lang.Object

SafraContainmentState is used in the on-the-fly containment testing with the Safra's construction. In a containment test whether the first automaton A is contained in the second automaton B or not, a SafraContainmentState represents a state in the complement of B.

Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
